    /// base_unit, and start_usage_amount to start_usage_amount in base_unit.
    /// unit_price / base_unit_conversion_factor = price per base_unit.
    /// start_usage_amount * base_unit_conversion_factor = start_usage_amount in
    /// base_unit.
